      <title>英国最新消息：失业率升至 2021 年中以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/uk-latest-unemployment-rises-to-highest-since-mid-2021</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国国家统计局周二表示，英国失业率意外升至两年半以来的最高水平，而私营部门的加薪压力有所缓解，进一步表明通胀压力正在减弱。彭博社的 Lizzy Burden 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/uk-latest-unemployment-rises-to-highest-since-mid-2021</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:28:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德青睐欧洲和英国债券，而非美国国债</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/blackrock-favors-european-uk-bonds-over-us-treasuries-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球首席投资策略师李炜表示，她更看好欧洲和英国政府债券，而非美国国债。她在彭博电视上表示：“我们喜欢前端和曲线的底部。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-11/blackrock-favors-european-uk-bonds-over-us-treasuries-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:15:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克通胀率下降，因决策者讨论放缓宽松步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/czech-inflation-drops-as-policymakers-debate-slower-easing-pace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克5月份通胀率降幅超过预期，但仍高于央行预测，因为政策制定者正在讨论本月是否放缓货币宽松步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/czech-inflation-drops-as-policymakers-debate-slower-easing-pace</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:15:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国利率不再受法国影响，欧洲股市重拾升势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/european-stocks-regain-ground-as-us-rates-take-focus-off-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人们的注意力从欧洲议会选举结果和法国政治不确定性加剧转向美国利率走势，欧洲股市上涨，收复失地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/european-stocks-regain-ground-as-us-rates-take-focus-off-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
